gr-atscmap
======

Author: Ron Economos
Email: <w6rz@comcast.net>

The goal of this project is to enable the use of the Nuand
FPGA based ATSC modulator and root-raised-cosine filter with
the standard osmosdr Sink block.

Build instructions:

    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ../
    make
    sudo make install
    sudo ldconfig

